in case you hit traffic.

378
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:37,829
<i>And I hope that your shiny new Mustang</i>

379
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:38,959
can get you here in time.

380
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,420
Drive safe now.

381
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:47,219
Okay. Where were we?

382
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:49,969
