383
00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:51,139
How is it?

384
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:53,470
Delicious.

385
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,489
Look here, motherfucker.

386
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:07,610
You...

387
00:22:10,410 --> 00:22:12,039
...you were right.

388
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:15,200
You were right the whole time.

389
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:18,499
I've-I've been out of line lately.

390
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:21,249
No, not just lately.

391
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:25,299
Ever since Maria died.

392
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:27,089
And I was pissed at you
for pointing it out.

393
00:22:27,090 --> 00:22:31,049
I was even more mad
when you tried to help me.

394
00:22:31,050 --> 00:22:36,229
I took our friendship,
our-our brotherhood for granted.

395
00:22:36,230 --> 00:22:40,189
Said some shit I can't come back from.

396
00:22:40,190 --> 00:22:43,189
And now, now, John,

397
00:22:43,190 --> 00:22:45,399
I-I'm not even here for the right reasons.

398
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:48,699
I should have come here
and looked you in your eye

399
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:51,950
