404
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:31,739
No. No, Elle. No, I'm serious.

405
00:23:31,740 --> 00:23:33,529
I-I do not date.

406
00:23:33,530 --> 00:23:36,119
I-I have acquaintances.

407
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:38,539
You know, I get acquainted.

408
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:40,789
- And then I get on up out of there.

409
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:42,750
Date.

410
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,169
So you never saw yourself settling down?

411
00:23:46,170 --> 00:23:47,670
No.

412
00:23:49,170 --> 00:23:50,509
I didn't see it for you, though.

413
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:55,849
Oh, Regina told me Alex pulled
some dumb shit, and you weren't having it,

414
00:23:55,850 --> 00:23:57,269
but let me tell you something.

415
00:23:57,270 --> 00:24:02,599
I have seen the way he looks at you,
and I've heard the way he talks about you.

416
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:06,480
It's real. It's worth fighting for.

417
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:13,109
Maybe one day you'll add some babies
of your own to the Cross family, huh?

418
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:14,569
Oh, we're there now?

419
00:24:14,570 --> 00:24:16,029
- Then, Miss Nancy,

420
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:18,079
