for something stronger than this tea.

421
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:21,909
Girl, I was wondering when you were
gonna join the party.

422
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:26,669
'Cause this whiskey here,
this is hitting the spot.

423
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:29,419
It's what we do at the cabin.

424
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:33,380
We drink, we eat, we try to keep warm.

425
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:38,059
Here you go.

426
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:39,889
Thank you.

427
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:45,560
To you and Alex working it out.

428
00:24:47,190 --> 00:24:49,230
Cheers.

429
00:24:55,450 --> 00:24:57,579
I can't believe it was her the whole time.

430
00:24:57,580 --> 00:24:58,699
Man, that woman's crazy.

431
00:24:58,700 --> 00:25:00,539
You realize how long
she must have been planning this?

432
00:25:00,540 --> 00:25:03,709
Just to get in the house
she had to volunteer for Early Mozart,

433
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:08,039
go to school, single Damon out,
convince Damon to...

434
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:10,799
Damn, man. And think about
all the times she was sitting

435
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:12,049
right next to you.

436
00:25:12,050 --> 00:25:13,629
I mean, why not just do it then?

437
00:25:13,630 --> 00:25:17,350
I don't know, John.
I'm afraid to find out.

438
00:25:51,670 --> 00:25:54,299
Jannie? Jannie, baby. Jannie.

439
00:25:54,300 --> 00:25:56,629
Hi. Come here, come here.

440
00:25:56,630 --> 00:25:59,349
- What's happening?
- It's time to go, baby, come on.

441
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,389
Come on. Watch your head.

442
00:26:00,390 --> 00:26:02,600
Here we go. Let's go, let's go, let's go.

443
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:11,900
