444
00:26:12,900 --> 00:26:14,740
This isn't about you.

445
00:26:15,820 --> 00:26:18,319
They're not your kids.

446
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:20,830
Get out of my way.

447
00:26:27,420 --> 00:26:28,460
Run!

448
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,170
Just go!

449
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,810
- Get in the back.

450
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:47,810
In the back, in the back.
Watch your head. Watch it.

451
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:51,610
Damon, keys.

452
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,489
No, no, no.

453
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:01,909
No, no. Run.

454
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:03,660
- Run! Run!

455
00:27:18,760 --> 00:27:20,219
We're about a mile out.

456
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:22,389
How long do you need?

457
00:27:22,390 --> 00:27:24,849
Once you get there,

458
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:27,849
