Bring the kids.

512
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:46,000
Good news is...

513
00:32:47,290 --> 00:32:49,960
...we only gonna take one.

514
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,180
And you get to choose.

515
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:57,180
So, which one will it be, Jannie...

516
00:32:58,430 --> 00:33:00,059
No, no.

517
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:01,479
...or Damon?

518
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:02,600
No, please.

519
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:07,979
No, N-Nancy, I can't answer that.

520
00:33:07,980 --> 00:33:11,149
You-you want revenge, kill me. Kill me!

521
00:33:11,150 --> 00:33:12,949
I'm not dead.

522
00:33:12,950 --> 00:33:15,569
I'm in agony.

523
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:19,199
Every minute of every hour of every day.

524
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:21,160
