525
00:33:23,290 --> 00:33:24,459
So pick one,

526
00:33:24,460 --> 00:33:26,079
I'll have Peter shoot that one.

527
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,999
- No, please.
- What?

528
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:30,630
It'll be over in an instant.

529
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:34,799
But you see, if you don't choose,

530
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:38,509
I will take them outside

531
00:33:38,510 --> 00:33:41,599
