533
00:33:44,980 --> 00:33:46,439
The kids haven't done anything.

534
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:48,359
He has to choose.

535
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,360
Why?

536
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:54,109
<i>He has to choose.</i>

537
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:56,029
Eye for an eye,

538
00:33:56,030 --> 00:33:58,199
she'd just kill one of them.

539
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:01,239
That's not justice for her.
She needs more.

540
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:03,199
It's the choice.

541
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:06,539
The choice.
Making me choose one of my own.

542
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:08,380
But why is that important?

543
00:34:09,590 --> 00:34:11,300
Unless...

544
