Right now
Peter's just a person of interest,

545
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,599
but we would like to speak with him.

546
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:23,599
If you do see him, let me know.

547
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:24,770
I sure will. Thank you.

548
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:29,440
- Hey, what'd they say?
- They're looking for Peter.

549
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,399
My God, they're going
to put him in prison.

550
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,739
He did it, right? So...

551
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:36,399
I know, I know. Oh, God.

552
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,779
With his record,

553
00:34:37,780 --> 00:34:39,950
they gonna bury that boy.

554
00:34:41,030 --> 00:34:43,119
Maybe even death sentence.

555
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:46,410
Oh, God. Oh, God.

556
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:50,710
But maybe there's a way
that we can help him.

557
00:34:52,340 --> 00:34:53,839
That you can help him.

558
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,009
How?

559
00:34:55,010 --> 00:34:58,509
What if there was a different suspect?

560
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:01,509
What if... what if someone else confessed?

561
