He broke her.

605
00:36:48,990 --> 00:36:51,289
She was broken by the time I met her.

606
00:36:51,290 --> 00:36:53,169
Going to prison snapped her.

607
00:36:53,170 --> 00:36:54,419
You did that.

608
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,079
