633
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,759
You don't have a choice.

634
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:08,679
Those were Maria's last words, Alex.

635
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:10,800
Or, at least, that's what I was told.

636
00:39:13,970 --> 00:39:15,429
You're gonna pay for this.

637
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:17,730
I'll pay in hell.

638
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,399
No! Mama!

639
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:24,899
Sugar, let's go! Come on!

640
00:39:24,900 --> 00:39:26,440
No! Mama!

641
00:39:29,450 --> 00:39:30,490
Sugar, let's go!

642
00:39:55,390 --> 00:39:56,469
