661
00:42:49,650 --> 00:42:52,690
<i>That's very kind of you, Alex,
but, no, thanks, I'm good.</i>

662
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:55,780
<i>Guys, come on.</i>

663
00:42:57,450 --> 00:42:58,910
