706
00:44:58,400 --> 00:45:00,939
<i>I'm confessing to all 11 kills, </i>

707
00:45:00,940 --> 00:45:04,109
all of which I have documented
in painstaking detail,

708
00:45:04,110 --> 00:45:07,079
