<i>Hey, John.</i>

715
00:45:21,460 --> 00:45:23,129
Hey.

716
00:45:23,130 --> 00:45:26,009
Can we get a look at that bookity-book?

717
00:45:26,010 --> 00:45:27,719
What is this?

718
00:45:27,720 --> 00:45:29,219
<i>Got it right here.</i>

719
00:45:29,220 --> 00:45:31,560
Does it look like this?

720
00:45:33,100 --> 00:45:34,439
Two John.

721
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,730
<i>Yeah.</i>

722
00:45:37,020 --> 00:45:38,359
Do it.

723
00:45:38,360 --> 00:45:40,900
<i>All right, then.</i>

724
00:45:44,320 --> 00:45:45,780
<i>Ooh, that's hot.</i>

725
00:45:47,570 --> 00:45:49,950
<i>Now, where should I start? Let me see...</i>

726
00:45:52,870 --> 00:45:54,750
<i>- Oh, this one's definitely got to go.</i>
- No.

727
00:45:55,830 --> 00:45:57,209
No!

728
00:45:57,210 --> 00:45:59,040
No, no, no!

729
00:46:01,300 --> 00:46:03,590
No! You can't do that!

730
00:46:04,590 --> 00:46:06,470
<i>You have to keep that, that's evidence!</i>

731
00:46:07,550 --> 00:46:12,270
No! It's evidence!

732
00:46:14,270 --> 00:46:16,310
<i>Those kills are mine!</i>

733
00:46:17,400 --> 00:46:19,229
<i>Paul David Harris, mine!</i>

734
00:46:19,230 --> 00:46:21,769
<i>Patricia Bennett, mine!</i>

735
00:46:21,770 --> 00:46:24,189
<i>Charles Anderson, mine!</i>

736
00:46:24,190 --> 00:46:26,239
<i>Donald Clark, mine!</i>

737
00:46:26,240 --> 00:46:29,119
That motherfucker is turnt all the way up.

738
00:46:29,120 --> 00:46:31,159
It's like he actually

739
00:46:31,160 --> 00:46:32,659
believes what he's saying.

740
00:46:32,660 --> 00:46:35,659
But we all know he's just crazy.

741
00:46:35,660 --> 00:46:39,379
<i>I will be remembered!
I will be remembered!</i>

742
00:46:39,380 --> 00:46:42,920
<i>I will be... I will be remembered!</i>

743
00:46:44,800 --> 00:46:46,340
<i>I will be remembered.</i>

744
00:46:47,300 --> 00:46:48,930
<i>I will be remembered.</i>

745
00:47:00,060 --> 00:47:02,150
You on surveillance detail?

746
00:47:03,360 --> 00:47:06,399
I'm looking for mermaids
with my granddaughter.

747
00:47:06,400 --> 00:47:09,109
I cured her of Santa Claus,

748
00:47:09,110 --> 00:47:12,240
but she truly believes Ariel's
gonna pop her head up any minute.

749
00:47:16,250 --> 00:47:18,459
How's the family? Regina?

750
00:47:18,460 --> 00:47:20,749
She's recovering.

751
00:47:20,750 --> 00:47:22,419
We all are.

752
00:47:22,420 --> 00:47:24,504
I wanted to give you
a heads-up about your hearing.

753
00:47:25,460 --> 00:47:26,800
You'll be cleared.

754
00:47:28,260 --> 00:47:30,589
- How?
- Victim took a settlement.

755
00:47:30,590 --> 00:47:32,679
Dropped all charges.

756
00:47:32,680 --> 00:47:34,639
So you can put that video behind you

757
00:47:34,640 --> 00:47:36,809
and move on.

758
00:47:36,810 --> 00:47:40,059
Well, if that is your "good news" face,
Alex, it needs some work.

759
00:47:40,060 --> 00:47:43,109
